msgid ""
"System will connect and clear all the attendance data in this machine. Are "
"you sure about this?"
msgstr ""
"El sistema se conectará y eliminará todos los datos de asistencia en este dispositivo. "
"¿Estás seguro de esto?"

msgid ""
"System will connect and download all the fingers template from your machine."
" Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"El sistema se conectará y descargará todas las plantillas de huellas del dispositivo. "
"¿Deseas continuar?"

msgid ""
"System will connect and download all the users from your machine (without "
"mapping those with the existing Employees in System). Do you want to "
"proceed?"
msgstr ""
"El sistema se conectará y descargará todos los usuarios del dispositivo (sin vincularlos con empleados existentes). "
"¿Deseas continuar?"

msgid ""
"System will connect and download all the users from your machine and try to "
"map those with the System's employees. Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"El sistema se conectará y descargará todos los usuarios del dispositivo e intentará vincularlos con los empleados del sistema. "
"¿Deseas continuar?"

msgid ""
"System will map the existing users with System's employees. The unmapped "
"employees will be uploaded to this machine as new users and then download "
"those new users into System and map them again with those unmapped "
"employees. Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"El sistema vinculará los usuarios existentes con los empleados. Los empleados no vinculados se subirán como nuevos usuarios y luego se descargarán para vincularlos nuevamente. "
"¿Deseas continuar?"

msgid ""
"System will try to map those with the System's employees. Do you want to "
"proceed?"
msgstr ""
"El sistema intentará vincularlos con los empleados del sistema. "
"¿Deseas continuar?"

